high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the sink.
Grab the fork and cup from the sink.
Place the fork and cup in the sink under the faucet.
anns.task_desc: Place a fork and cup under the sink faucet.

high_descs: Move to the left hand side of the kitchen sink where the fork and cup are
Pick up the cup and fork on the counter left of the sink that are furthest left
Carry the fork and cup to face the sink basin
Place the cup and fork in the sink basin
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and fork to the sink

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Grab the frying pan off the sink's counter.
Place the frying pan under the faucet.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan from the counter to the sink.
